  <!-- SECTION: SANCTUARY -->
  <section class="section sanctuary-section" id="sanctuary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sanctuary-inner">
        <span class="section-tag">06 / Beyond the Music</span>
        <blockquote class="sanctuary-quote">
          <p>Circuit music is only one dimension of the circuit party. Beneath the sound, the spectacle, and the physical release lies something deeper: sanctuary. In a world where queer people have too often faced shame, persecution, and even death simply for existing, the circuit party can become an act of collective euphoria and remembrance, a temporary refuge where bodies are not hidden, love is not explained, and belonging does not need permission. For a moment, people step into a world shaped by one another, before returning to one that has not always offered the same grace.</p>
          <footer class="sanctuary-attribution">— Curtis Baldwinson</footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
